Package prkmodel.types

Interface NervousSystem

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultNervousSystem, RepastNervousSystem
public interface NervousSystem
Interface representing the nervous system. It defines the structure and functionalities of the nervous system in the simulation.
Since:
2024-07-03
Version:
1.0
Author:
Samuele95
